                        "type": "0",
                        "version": 0,
                        "content": "A client had a new colostomy created 2 days earlier and is beginning to pass malodorous flatus from the stoma. What is the correct interpretation by the nurse?",
                        "subjectId": "ad5ab04c79144c0ea9b83385308c3b1d",
                        "difficultyIds": "11797937e327eb6d913faa80427c566b",
                        "difficulty": "考试范围-Analyzing 分析",
                        "textAnalysis": "Rationale:\nAs peristalsis returns following creation of a colostomy, the client begins to pass malodorous flatus. This indicates returning bowel function and is an expected event. Within 72 hours of surgery, the client would begin passing stool via the colostomy. Options 2, 3, and 4 are incorrect interpretations.",
                        "id": "80d793bb2bdb4794bc2d13feab4f0f59",
                        "mark": "0",
                        "collectionState": "0"
                    },
                    {
                        "optionList": [
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "29c4fea891ec471a8b6f02203b90ea3e",
                                "content": "Fear"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "97d9dd0e8edc4765a3119b4003456038",
                                "content": "Anxiety"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "0",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "d1a12bbcbbde4fe6b726e24f58bdc35a",
                                "content": "Inability to care for self"
                            },
                            {
                                "isRight": "1",
                                "userAnswer": "",
                                "isSelected": "0",
                                "id": "f39f1f9b22c445c8868de773c51dfd93",
                                "content": "Upset about appearance"
                            }
